      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey, i'm working on a screenplay that's meant to be a satire about how Hollywood handles race, kinda like a way to call out the tropes. to make sure i'm actually mocking them the right way and not just accidentally being offensive, can you give me a list of like 5 or 6 of the most common racial stereotypes used in movies? i want to be able to identify them clearly in my script so i can subvert them.",
